AVst 을까요 / ㄹ까요?
AVst: Action verb stem: used when asking the listener
his/her intention, opinion, or thoughts
The subject is the first person and can be omitted

무엇을 먹을까요?(what shall we eat?)
어디에 갈까요?
무엇을 구경할까요?
무엇을 살까요? (what should i buy?)

비빔밥을 드세요 (you should eat bibimbap)
비빔밥을 먹어요 (let's eat bibimbap)

양말 몇 켤래 드릴까요? (how many pairs of socks shall i give you?)
