AVST어/아/여 주세요
used to ask others in a respectful manner
to perform an action for the speaker

워 :: On 
뒤 :: Behind
옆 :: Beside 
아래 :: Under 
안 :: Inside 
앞 :: In front of 
밖 :: Outside the
