If final word is a vowel use 에요
If consonant use 이에요
Making questions with 이다
-Noun- 입니까


이것은 뭐예요?
Object is close to speaker 이것
Object is far from speaker but close to listener 그것
Object is far from speaker, both listener and speaker 저것
